Grammar

    0 $accept: program $end

    1 program: preprocessor_list main_function

    2 preprocessor_list: preprocessor_list preprocessor
    3                  | ε

    4 preprocessor: INCLUDE HEADER
    5             | DEFINE IDENTIFIER INT_LITERAL

    6 main_function: MAIN LPAREN RPAREN LBRACE statement_list RBRACE

    7 statement_list: statement_list statement
    8               | ε

    9 statement: declaration
   10          | assignment SEMI
   11          | array_assignment SEMI
   12          | print_stmt
   13          | scan_stmt
   14          | if_stmt
   15          | switch_stmt
   16          | BREAK SEMI
   17          | loop_stmt
   18          | return_stmt SEMI

   19 declaration: type identifier_list_decls SEMI
   20            | type IDENTIFIER LBRACKET array_size RBRACKET SEMI
   21            | type IDENTIFIER LBRACKET array_size RBRACKET LBRACKET array_size RBRACKET SEMI

   22 array_size: INT_LITERAL

   23 type: INT_TYPE
   24     | FLOAT_TYPE
   25     | DOUBLE_TYPE
   26     | CHAR_TYPE
   27     | BOOL_TYPE
   28     | VOID_TYPE
   29     | LONG_TYPE
   30     | SHORT_TYPE
   31     | UNSIGNED_TYPE

   32 identifier_list_decls: IDENTIFIER
   33                      | IDENTIFIER ASSIGN expression
   34                      | IDENTIFIER COMMA identifier_list_decls
   35                      | IDENTIFIER ASSIGN expression COMMA identifier_list_decls

   36 assignment: IDENTIFIER ASSIGN expression

   37 array_assignment: IDENTIFIER LBRACKET expression RBRACKET ASSIGN expression
   38                 | IDENTIFIER LBRACKET expression RBRACKET LBRACKET expression RBRACKET ASSIGN expression

   39 expression: expression PLUS term
   40           | expression MINUS term
   41           | MINUS term
   42           | term

   43 term: term MUL factor
   44     | term DIV factor
   45     | term MOD factor
   46     | factor

   47 factor: primary

   48 primary: IDENTIFIER
   49        | INT_LITERAL
   50        | FLOAT_LITERAL
   51        | TRUE_LITERAL
   52        | FALSE_LITERAL
   53        | CHAR_LITERAL
   54        | LPAREN expression RPAREN
   55        | function_call
   56        | array_access

   57 array_access: IDENTIFIER LBRACKET expression RBRACKET
   58             | IDENTIFIER LBRACKET expression RBRACKET LBRACKET expression RBRACKET

   59 function_call: POW LPAREN expression COMMA expression RPAREN
   60              | SQRT LPAREN expression RPAREN
   61              | ABS LPAREN expression RPAREN
   62              | FLOOR LPAREN expression RPAREN
   63              | CEIL LPAREN expression RPAREN

   64 print_stmt: PRINT LPAREN STRING_LITERAL RPAREN SEMI
   65           | PRINT LPAREN IDENTIFIER RPAREN SEMI
   66           | PRINT LPAREN expression RPAREN SEMI

   67 scan_stmt: SCAN LPAREN IDENTIFIER RPAREN SEMI
   68          | SCAN LPAREN IDENTIFIER LBRACKET expression RBRACKET RPAREN SEMI

   69 condition: expression EQ expression
   70          | expression NEQ expression
   71          | expression GT expression
   72          | expression LT expression
   73          | expression GE expression
   74          | expression LE expression

   75 if_stmt: IF LPAREN condition RPAREN LBRACE statement_list RBRACE else_if_part

   76 else_if_part: ELSEIF LPAREN condition RPAREN LBRACE statement_list RBRACE else_if_part
   77             | ELSE LBRACE statement_list RBRACE
   78             | ε

   79 switch_stmt: SWITCH LPAREN expression RPAREN LBRACE case_list RBRACE

   80 case_list: case_list case_item
   81          | case_list default_item
   82          | ε

   83 case_item: CASE case_expr COLON statement_list

   84 case_expr: expression
   85          | expression RANGE expression

   86 default_item: DEFAULT COLON statement_list

   87 for_update: assignment

   88 loop_stmt: WHILE LPAREN condition RPAREN LBRACE statement_list RBRACE
   89          | FOR LPAREN assignment SEMI condition SEMI for_update RPAREN LBRACE statement_list RBRACE

   90 return_stmt: RETURN expression


